Topic Selection & Objectives
  Work Done: Finalized project topic “Spam Email Detection.” Defined objectives:

Build a machine learning model to classify emails/messages as spam or ham.

Analyze dataset and preprocessing methods.

Evaluate performance with metrics like accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score.

Why/How: Selecting a clear topic ensures focus and measurable outcomes.

Learned: Planning helps to organize the tasks for a 30-day workflow.
